Survival Outcomes in Octogenarian and Nonagenarian Patients Treated with 
First-line Androgen Deprivation Therapy for Organ-confined Prostate Cancer.

Dell'Oglio P(1), Bishr M(2), Boehm K(3), Trudeau V(2), Larcher A(4), Tian Z(5), 
Sosa J(6), Moschini M(4), Saad F(7), Capitanio U(4), Briganti A(4), Graefen 
