Efficacy and Safety of Human Intravenous Immunoglobulin 10% (Panzyga®) in 
Patients with Primary Immunodeficiency Diseases: a Two-Stage, Multicenter, 
Prospective, Open-Label Study.

Borte M(1)(2), Melamed IR(3), Pulka G(4), Pyringer B(5), Knutsen AP(6), Ochs 
HD(7), Kobayashi RH(8), Kobayashi AL(9), Gupta S(10), Strach M(11), Smits W(12), 
Pituch-Noworolska A(13), Moy JN(14).

Author information:
(1)Klinik für Kinder- und Jugendmedizin, Klinikum St. Georg gGmbH, Leipzig, 
Germany. Michael.Borte@sanktgeorg.de.
(2)Immunodeficiency Centre Leipzig (IDCL), Hospital St. Georg gGmbH Leipzig, 
